<title>Filtering Cases and Display Options</title>

<subheader>Filtering Cases</subheader>

To view a subset of the cases in the data file, you can enter a search query to filter the cases shown. The query will only filter by case IDs, not case labels. Enter the query and press <b>Enter</b> or click on the search icon. For example, this query would show only cases whose ID begins with '02':

